      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 8 article, which misstated name of Nighline's new executive producer: he is Leroy Sievers</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day yesterday about the decision of Ted Koppel, anchor of ABC News's ''Nightline,'' to sign a new five-year contract with the program misstated the given name of a new executive producer who will oversee it. He is Leroy Sievers, not Tom.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article in Business Day yesterday about the decision of Ted Koppel, anchor of ABC News's ''Nightline,'' to sign a new five-year contract with the program misstated the given name of a new executive producer who will oversee it. He is Leroy Sievers, not Tom.</p>
      </block>
